的 plan b 也能被看见。」数学老师说姜萍属于勤奋型选手"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-fc4a9ffa5ccb6d66b82c953490e506f8_1440w.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658889523"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI75iI7Y/6z5MWEAMaCTEwODY5Nzg1OSCNn6+zBjAAOJQCQBZyCTY1ODg4OTUyM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1718460509.653984", "card_id": "Q_656171156", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "汽车熄火听歌可以听多久?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-2510b494e2d59a4073e8fb816c566a94_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/656171156"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I75iI7Y/6z5MWEAMaCTEwODA5MzcwNSCixJWyBjAAOENAF3IJNjU2MTcxMTU2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1718460509.654760", "card_id": "Q_658896273", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 75}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "河北邯郸宣布购买新房给予 1 % 购房补贴，多孩家庭公积金贷款额最高 100 万元 ，透露了哪些信息？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "河北邯郸近日发布关于优化房地产政策的若干措施。在实施购房补贴方面，对购买新建商品住房的购房人按照成交价的 1% 给予购房补贴；对到企业入职的高校毕业生、生育二胎及以上家庭、 60 岁及以上老人购买新建商品住房的，购房补贴额再上调 0.5%。此外，落实住房贷款支持政策。首套、二套住房商贷最低首付款比例分别调整为不低于 15% 、 25%，个人住房公积金贷款利率下调 0.25 个百分点。同时，提高公积金贷款最高限额，「二孩」「三孩」家庭分别提高至 80 万元、 100 万元。河北邯郸：购买新房给予 1% 购房补贴，多孩家庭公积金贷款额最高 100 万元 _ 住房 _ 政策 _ 商品"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8fdda6a8e6ef326c7de37bbbb6ba1338_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "norm